    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect the following types of personal information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Your name and email address when you register for an account</li>
        <li>Your payment information when you make a purchase</li>
        <li>Your IP address, browser type, and operating system when you use our platform</li>
        <li>Your usage data, such as the courses you take and your progress, when you use our services</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your personal information for the following purposes:</p>
