        <li>To comply with legal and regulatory requirements</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Share Your Information</h2>
    <p>We may share your personal information with the following third parties:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Service providers who help us provide our services, such as hosting and payment processing</li>
        <li>Law enforcement or government agencies when required by law or to protect our legal rights</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>
        We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, and disclosure. However, no security measures are perfect and we
        cannot guarantee the security of your information.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on our platform.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
